Sentencas: La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag hollow nanofibers are successfully prepared by electro-spinning technology.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag Hollow Nanofibers

Sentencas: The phase and morphology of the materials are characterized by XRD and SEM.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag Hollow Nanofibers

Sentencas: The results show that La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag hollow nanofibers with an average diameter in 400 nm are obtained after sintering at 800 degrees C for 2 h. The La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag nanofiber forms mesh-like morphology and good contact with the electrolyte after sintering at 850 degrees C for 1 h. The Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy (EIS) measurements show that the area specific resistance (ASR) of La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag nanofiber cathode is 0.32 cm(2)at 700 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag Hollow Nanofibers

Sentencas: The oxygen partial pressure measurement indicates that the rate limiting step of the nanofiber cathode is charge transfer process from 600 to 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of La1.6Sr0.4NiO4-Ag Hollow Nanofibers
